Manus,

I have an idea for the Pouch Zine. I bet there are a lot of people out there who 
have thought about writing an article on something or other, but have decided 
against it because they don't think they can make it long enough to be worth it. 
Therefore, how about :

"Pouch Paragraphs".

The idea is simple. People each write a one-paragraph article, and then they all 
go together to make one item in the main Zine menu. This has two advantages. 
Firstly, you get an extra article for the Pouch every issue. Secondly, I bet 
several people will start writing their "Pouch Paragraph", write two or three 
pages without realising it, and hey presto, you have another complete article.

Howzat ?

David.
